                        ShlinkMarket <span
                            class="text-sm italic text-gray-500">Because you're
                            worth it.</span>
                    </h1>
                    <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        Spend your ShlinkPoints on ads. Each ad has a limited
                        quantity, so act fast!

                    </span>

                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main>
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
